{"title":"蔗海短歌（三首）","authors":["洪三泰"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":8,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔗海短歌（三首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪三泰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔗　芽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饥渴、干裂的红土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吸饱春雨，吱吱地笑了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"露出甘蔗细嫩的芽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吮吸汗水的苦涩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨露的清凉……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芽呵，出土有节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"节节香甜……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海鸥迷路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海鸥盘旋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓦然迷落蔗海。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啪，啪，啪，啪……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扇起绿浪层层……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腾空南飞时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟带去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一双双甜蜜的翅膀……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔗镰的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘶啦，嘶啦，嘶啦……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰给蔗唱壮烈的歌："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺立时，聚成蔗海。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒下了，堆成蔗山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"榨碎了，流成糖河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熬干了，垒起糖峰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘶啦，嘶啦，嘶啦……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔗给镰唱自己的心歌。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}